msgid "Already a Spring pro? You're in the right place. This guide shows you how to leverage your existing skills to build next-generation Java applications. Ditch the slow startup times and heavy memory footprint without ditching your knowledge. See how familiar concepts like DI, JPA, and MVC map directly to Quarkus and get ready to build cloud native, AI-infused apps."
msgstr ""

